                        <h3>Alpha Show</h3>
                        <span class="price">45€</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>The ultimate Albanian music experience.</p>
                    <div class="event-info">
                        <p>August 12, 2025</p>
                        <p>Durres, Albania</p>
